metadata.name: Bitcino Platinum #1
metadata.description:
This token represents your ownership of membership to Bitcino.
As a Bitcino member, you will be eligible to different benefits when you visit the bar.
This token is also a collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain.
After purchasing on NFT marketplaces, please create a profile at app.moongate.id and connect your wallet to verify ownership of your token. You can then present the QR code associated with the Bitcino Platinum #1.
